                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Telegram 2868, November 14, from Paris, page 1664, reported that at a meeting of
                    the tripartite working group on Germany’s financial contribution to Western
                    defense, attended by American and British observers to the Conference on a
                    European Defense Community, <persName corresp="#p_AH1">Alphand</persName>
                    outlined a proposal for an interim European Defense Community common budget
                    which the French intended to introduce at the Conference.</p>
            </div>
